<refsection>
<title>Extensions</title>

<para>XML Calabash implements an extension to the <tag>p:exec</tag> step.</para>

<para>The <tag>cx:show-stderr</tag> extension attribute controls whether or
not process output to <literal>STDERR</literal> is displayed as the process
runs.</para>

<para>If <option>errors-is-xml</option> is <literal>true</literal>, this
extension attribute is ignored.</para>
